BTrackMate v2.0.0 BTrackmate is a slim version of Trackmate If you input label images/csv file we skip detection process of Trackmate. Made for Claudia Carabana Garcia by Varun Kapoor, TrackMate is based on: Tinevez, JY.; Perry, N. & Schindelin, J. et al. (2017), 'TrackMate: An open and extensible platform for single-particle tracking.', Methods 115: 80-90, PMID 27713081. https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/27713081 https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1046202316303346
Numerical feature analyzers: Spot feature analyzers: - Manual spot color provides: Spot color; is manual. - Spot intensity provides: Mean ch1, Median ch1, Min ch1, Max ch1, Sum ch1, Std ch1. - Spot contrast and SNR provides: Ctrst ch1, SNR ch1.
